#. Tag: para
#: Websphere.xml:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to use component injection, Seam needs to know how to lookup for "
"session beans bound to the JNDI name space. Seam provides two mechanisms to "
"configure the way it will search for such resources:"
